      "name": "ASTM F1717 static compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "Valid operating envelope: axial compressive load 0–4500 N applied at 5 mm/min crosshead displacement rate; bending moment arm 60 mm (ASTM F1717 standard geometry); ambient temperature 23 ± 2 °C; UHMWPE block density 930–940 kg/m³; rod diameter 5.5 mm CoCr; construct span 26 mm. Extrapolation outside these bounds—particularly to rod diameters outside 5.0–6.0 mm or loading rates exceeding 50 mm/min—is not covered by this assessment."
    }
